snippet.title: Sounds of Color, Happy Music, Uplifting, Relaxing Original by Amber Crowley Singer Songwriter, 2021
snippet.description:
Have you ever heard the Sounds of Color? We have right here: Sounds of Color is Happy Music, Uplifting and Relaxing Original Song by Amber Crowley, Singer Songwriter. This song is about the Colors of Sound Waves that make up our Music. Family friendly, clean lyric, acoustic folk pop music. Her songs reflect her love of the environment. Her lyrics convey thoughtful messages of hope, love, Diversity and Peace. Thank you so much for listening, commenting, and subscribing. So grateful for you!
"Sounds of Color" is from Amber Crowley's Album "Amber Waves"@2020. Recorded at Bruce Maclean Studio, Orleans, Massachusetts.
